{"tid":958452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【估國家】女保險經紀涉狎男友兒子：啜耳珠、捽心口、彈陽具","createTime":"2018-12-27T21:48:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T05:28:28.000Z","uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8301e484c4f0ffec6e05fb4b28fe7b7dade3c8ac","tid":958452,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T21:48:44.000Z","msg":"事發於今年2月4日晚，X憶述被告穿着看似浴袍的睡衣，和他一同摺衫。被告突稱有家事想與X商討，帶X入睡房，一同坐在X的梳化床上。其間被告稱感到很凍，把身軀貼近X，「越瞓越過」，並稱「你大個要媾女」便從後攬他。<br />\n<br />\nX稱被告先是像吮手指般啜他耳珠十多秒，弄得「成隻耳仔都係口水」，繼而摸他肚腩及捽心口幾秒。被告一直說很凍，再直接伸手入X的內褲之中，摸及彈其陽具，為時十多秒。X在錄影中稱，事前見被告喝過紅酒，認為她可能飲醉。X續說，翌日回校向社工講述事件經過，亦有向同學透露自己「被阿媽性侵犯」，但遭取笑。"},{"pid":"f1bd906e7a31f2d81631532d88f828d15118034b","tid":958452,"uid":119363,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T21:51:10.000Z","msg":"文筆咁香港嘅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我估香港"},{"pid":"e29d01c4960067fe1db8b789e6b3223e14ea3896","tid":958452,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T22:01:51.000Z","msg":"日本"},{"pid":"dcd32c564650ce34aa1cac5d2f65a363841469e6","tid":958452,"uid":158270,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T22:03:55.000Z","msg":"你係咪掙d嘢"},{"pid":"f4d4f094cede070574291852950f0b3757fac567","tid":958452,"uid":221132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T22:04:37.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"d47e7f25d39eb0b9c993ee6ac754fa222a6f9906","tid":958452,"uid":124785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T22:05:50.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"1e12d7f938981131a930d340b31cba05ee6c72de","tid":958452,"uid":187298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T22:08:53.000Z","msg":"咪香港囉 尋日熱門有啦"},{"pid":"3e699ce61fbed2f7a1fdff325fb1d560b0a1c7cc","tid":958452,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T22:25:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係咪掙d嘢</blockquote><br />\n無圖。報紙都無圖。"},{"pid":"b8785b769da428921f8a530f731135719ffcbc6c","tid":958452,"uid":49392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T22:57:24.000Z","msg":"要搞就搞我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8d68bcc415a8a18a85351571a30ea65785dd80","tid":958452,"uid":13936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T23:09:24.000Z","msg":"咁撚正既機會都講比人知<br />\n將來佢大個 一定後悔無食"},{"pid":"7675d9c49589c8fcbf751465659cb3f95b3ff4c3","tid":958452,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T23:57:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁撚正既機會都講比人知<br />\n將來佢大個 一定後悔無食</blockquote><br />\n十歲太細，如果十三四歲就肯定會食埋後母"},{"pid":"27e68c1d2523faa90f9e646c9b46df960d1fa70d","tid":958452,"uid":49664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T05:28:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e0ekYLN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe0ekYLN.gif&h=b1dfbed1&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}